- Use React functional components with hooks.
- Avoid class components entirely.
- Style with CSS Modules or Tailwind.
- Animate transitions using CSS or Framer Motion for hover and tap effects.
- Store user-defined filters using chrome.storage.local (not localStorage).
- Persist the filter input across page reloads using the Chrome Extension API.
- Show a right caret icon on each request row that navigates to a detail screen.
- In the detail screen, allow copying individual headers.
- Include copy buttons for request body and response body below each API entry in the list.
- Follow Chrome Extension Manifest V3 architecture.
